{"tid":1713812,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"台仔教路（有無人知點解要攻打中大？）","createTime":"2019-11-12T20:23:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-13T03:11:11.000Z","uid":239389,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"d9a4aa4b7f9aff7a361c288c9a6facb763df1eda","tid":1713812,"uid":239389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T20:23:02.000Z","msg":"「各位在中大奮戰的朋友，今夜包括我在內有許多台灣人也一夜難眠。有許多評論指這是六四再版，但如我卻想到1949的四六事件，有一點事情可以跟各位分享：<br />\n<br />\n1、雖然台灣不曾有黑警強攻大學的歷史，但情治機關一直能牢牢掌控校園，靠的正是校方高層出賣學生的合作態度。<br />\n<br />\n2、當時的台大與師大校長同意軍警進入校園搜捕參與運動的學生，導致數名學生遭到判刑甚至槍決。<br />\n<br />\n3、校方更進一步「整頓校風」，勒令解散社團、開除支持學生的教師，迎接長達數十年的校園戒嚴。<br />\n<br />\n4、這件事情對台灣的知識份子養成造成劇烈的影響，有很多代的社會菁英不敢反抗國民黨，成為國民黨至今的統治根基。台灣出產的郭位正是這個時代背景的惡果。<br />\n<br />\n5、今夜黑警對中大的攻城戰，不僅象徵無底線的暴行，更代表他們想開始「整頓校風」，要控制接下來數個世代的社會菁英。<br />\n<br />\n大家務必要守住校園，慎防校方出賣學生、出賣香港的未來。」<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.twmemory.org/?p=11055\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.twmemory.org%2F%3Fp%3D11055&d=QaIhKqS2ROfvs0VeIWBCOq7%2FPCTF2%2B9SGuy7I2Db2XM%3D&h=e5cdedae\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.twmemory.org/?p=11055</a>"},{"pid":"2dad3b87dc619e6eaf684a396597d578b2ed23bd","tid":1713812,"uid":69221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T20:24:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b4f47fcdba32346a0ee1824a352f6dd6cefeb8fb","tid":1713812,"uid":23180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T20:29:12.000Z","msg":"同感"},{"pid":"58c879d1f91a4c93b5fe88f81fa386d1816fff9b","tid":1713812,"uid":151544,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T20:30:16.000Z","msg":"Cityu 同學真係慘"},{"pid":"3a495bafa9e6132b7d7b3e34abacf2e2cb74454a","tid":1713812,"uid":292987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T20:34:35.000Z","msg":"國共手段一致 就係消滅一代菁英 令到成個社會消音 廿年內個統治冇人可以挑戰"},{"pid":"86f6748988c790b46a4b6682354817341bfd64e5","tid":1713812,"uid":239389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T03:09:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"deed44e5954b5147a694029009a1a9097da633f2","tid":1713812,"uid":39492,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"58c879d1f91a4c93b5fe88f81fa386d1816fff9b","tid":1713812,"uid":151544,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T20:30:16.000Z","msg":"Cityu 同學真係慘"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T03:11:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />係。中大都叫有校長、副校為佢哋企前線、做談判⋯⋯<br />\nCity U乜春都冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}